    <item>
      <title>皮尔亨特称英国小盘股指数濒临灭绝</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/a-uk-stock-index-is-on-track-for-extinction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦股票经纪人 Peel Hunt Ltd 警告称，如果目前的收购活动水平持续下去且首次公开募股市场未能反弹，那么到 2028 年，英国小盘股指数将不复存在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/a-uk-stock-index-is-on-track-for-extinction</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 10:26:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油市场正处于风险升级的环境中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-03/oil-market-is-in-an-escalatory-risk-environment-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 OPEC+ 会议之前，Rapidan Energy 创始人鲍勃·麦克纳利 (Bob McNally) 认为，由于地缘政治紧张局势带来的“风险升级”，油价上涨 40 美元的可能性为 30%，本周伊朗声称以色列杀害了其在叙利亚的指挥官。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-03/oil-market-is-in-an-escalatory-risk-environment-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 10:26:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Blue Owl 将在最新保险交易中收购 Kuvare Asset Management</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/blue-owl-to-buy-kuvare-asset-management-in-latest-insurance-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Blue Owl Capital Inc. 已同意收购 Kuvare Asset Management，这一最新交易凸显了私募市场投资公司在保险市场上开发资产池的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/blue-owl-to-buy-kuvare-asset-management-in-latest-insurance-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 10:21:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>NFL 头盔制造商 Riddell 从 BC Partners 获得 4 亿美元投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/nfl-helmet-maker-riddell-gets-400-million-from-bc-partners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社看到的一份声明，BC Partners 的信贷部门同意向橄榄球头盔制造商 Riddell 提供 4 亿美元，这笔交易将为包括私募股权公司 Fenway Partners 在内的股东带来期待已久的付款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/nfl-helmet-maker-riddell-gets-400-million-from-bc-partners</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pimco加大了对美联储降息幅度低于全球同行的债券押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/pimco-boosts-bond-bets-that-fed-will-cut-less-than-global-peers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[太平洋投资管理公司的安德鲁·鲍尔斯表示，债券市场押注美联储在未来几年降息幅度将低于其他主要央行的时机已经成熟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/pimco-boosts-bond-bets-that-fed-will-cut-less-than-global-peers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港放宽改变身份证性别的手术要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/hong-kong-eases-surgery-requirement-for-changing-sex-on-id-cards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港放宽了对跨性别者的一些规定，以便改变官方身份证上的性别，但仍保留强制进行某些类型手术的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/hong-kong-eases-surgery-requirement-for-changing-sex-on-id-cards</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 09:49:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元区通胀逼近 2%，六月降息为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/euro-area-inflation-inches-toward-2-keeping-focus-on-june-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区通胀放缓幅度超出预期，巩固了欧洲央行六月份降息的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/euro-area-inflation-inches-toward-2-keeping-focus-on-june-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国放宽汽车贷款规则以刺激消费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/china-moves-to-boost-ev-sector-by-relaxing-auto-loan-ratios</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中国希望通过其庞大的汽车行业提振疲软的消费者信心，中国放宽了购买私家车的贷款难度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/china-moves-to-boost-ev-sector-by-relaxing-auto-loan-ratios</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 08:26:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在鲍威尔发表讲话之前，黄金价格从新纪录回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/gold-hits-record-as-silver-surges-on-outlook-for-fed-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名美联储官员表示，他们仍预计美联储今年将降息三次，主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔将于周三晚些时候发表讲话，金价从新纪录回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/gold-hits-record-as-silver-surges-on-outlook-for-fed-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 01:53:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
